title: Oven-Ready Chicken & Gnocchi Bake with Marinara Sauce & Italian Herbs
description: Weeknights feeling busier and more jam-packed than ever? We hear you! That’s why we’re bringing you our quickest, easiest meals yet. Introducing Oven-Ready Dinners. All you have to do is assemble in our aluminum trays, pop ’em in the oven, and dig in! No need to worry about prep or dirtying multiple dishes. This week, we’re featuring pillowy potato gnocchi in a buttery marinara sauce, topped with cheesy, panko-crusted chicken and a sprinkle of chili flakes. Think it can’t get any better? It’s all ready in 30 minutes or less—yes, you really can have it all.
